### 10. Google Apps Script

#### [NEW] Apps Script Code

Saya akan menyediakan kode lengkap Apps Script yang perlu di-upload ke spreadsheet, meliputi:

**Endpoints:**

| Method | Endpoint | Fungsi |
|--------|----------|--------|
| GET | `?action=getActivities&periode=2026-06-14` | Ambil kegiatan per periode |
| GET | `?action=getPeriods` | Daftar semua periode yang ada |
| GET | `?action=getSuggestions&periode=2026-06-14` | Ambil kegiatan yang sudah ada untuk suggest |
| POST | `action=addActivity` | Tambah kegiatan baru |
| POST | `action=generateSummary` | Generate AI summary via Gemini |

**Flow Apps Script:**
1. `doGet(e)` — Handle GET requests
2. `doPost(e)` — Handle POST requests
3. `getActivities(periode)` — Query sheet berdasarkan periode
4. `addActivity(data)` — Insert row ke sheet
5. `generateSummary(activities)` — Panggil Gemini API dan return summary

